Unit 8: Passive Voice / Participles as Adjectives Unit 9: How can a small amount of money make a big difference? In-class listening task 1: Can money buy you happiness?give something away counter-intuitive charityincome brand-newset the precedent In-class listening task 2: listen and complete the summarySophy: If you ______________, a small amount of money can become a large amount of money.Felix: I can give a small amount of money to someone _________________.Marcus: If we put our money together, a small amount for each person will make a big difference for the ___________. Yuna: I can buy something that _____________, like comfortable _________. 






期中評量

                    
                    
  
  
  
  
  posted 8 Apr 2014, 00:30 by Chingliang Shih

                    
                  

考試範圍涵蓋教科書第八單元。測驗形式為閱讀理解，共三篇文章。其中一篇取自課本的課文，另一篇是線上練習(Q Online Practice) 出現的文章，第三篇是你沒看過的新文章，但其主題都與本單元相關。測驗題型式：是非、字彙、副標配合、閱讀理解選擇題。






