 New Zero-Carbon City 2-3 (p.159-60)Paragraph 2The first part of this project is the construction of one of...The first part of this project is to construct one of....This plant will provide most of the energy for the entire cityThis plant will provide the entire city __________ most of the energy.energy plant / power plant 發電廠It will be home to more than 50,000 people.It will a____________ more than 50,000 people. Paragraph 3Masdar city will be unique not only in its sustainability, but in many other ways. within the city's walls ...recycling is central to the development of the city.recycled materials 回收過的材料, 在此recycled當做形容詞用 






